Pigeon Forge, Tennessee

Valley Forge Inn Rooms & Amenities

Our Amenities Include:

  • Refrigerator, Microwave, Coffee Maker, Hair Dryer, Iron and Ironing Board In Every Room
  • WiFi Internet Access Available
  • Indoor Pool with Hot-Tub
  • Outdoor Pool with Kiddie Pool
  • Gas Fireplaces Available
  • In-room Jacuzzi's Available
  • Private Balcony Views of Parkway or Little Pigeon River
  • Remote control TV's with over 75 Cable Channels
  • In-room Voice Mail/Messaging Service
  • Continental Breakfast Included
  • Guest Laundry Facilities
  • Elevators
  • Two-level Townhouses Available
  • Large Family Suites Available
  • Sunday Afternoon Worship Service in Breakfast Room
  • Sorry, No Pets

Here at the Valley Forge Inn, we have several different room types to fit your needs. From a room with a king bed for 2 people, a family suite that will sleep 6-8 people, to Two-Level Townhouses!

For room rates and availability please call us at 1-800-544-8740. The lines are open 24 hours a day to help plan your stay in Pigeon Forge. Please be ready to specify the number of adults and children, plus the date of arrival and departure. Online Reservations Coming Soon!

Valley Forge Inn

Valley Forge Inn Location & Attractions

Location & Map:

The Valley Forge Inn is located on the main parkway, US Hwy 441 between traffic light 3 & 4 next to the Happy Days Diner and the Comedy Barn In the Heart of Pigeon Forge, Tennessee.

 

Area Attractions:

The Valley Forge Inn is Conveniently located to the many great area attractions that Pigeon Forge, Sevierville, and Gatlinburg Tennessee have to offer. We are within walking distance to many attractions and restaurants, and it is just a short drive to the Great Smoky Mountains National Park. Below are just a few of the great area attractions you can visit while staying at the Valley Forge Inn.

  • Dollywood
  • Dollywood Splash Country
  • Comedy Barn
